# Branded client content

- Per-client **voice, services, and visual DNA** live in Streamlit/SQLite (`brand_context`, `tone`, `services_list`, `target_markets`) and in **`docs/brands/*.md`**.
- **Alberton Tyre Clinic:** follow `docs/brands/alberton-tyre-clinic.md` — Tyre Orange `#F17924`, dark charcoal premium garage imagery, heritage/safety copy (since 1989, Alberton), no discount-yard tone unless explicitly briefed.
- When changing `tasks.yaml` / `agents.yaml`, keep **generic** rules in YAML; put **client-specific** lines only in brand markdown + CRM paste blocks.
- After editing a brand doc, sync CRM via UI or `uv run python scripts/upsert_alberton_brand.py`.
